msgid ""
"If you prefer Theora (which you probably don’t since Ogg Video usually"
" causes problems), you can alternatively download"
" ::download:`kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2 <"
"/files/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2>`."
