msgid ""
"To be correct, it *can* be played using ``melt yourproject.kdenlive``,"
" but this is not the way you would want to present your final video since"
" it is (most likely) too slow. Additionally, it only works if melt is"
" installed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../getting_started/quickstart.rst:280
msgid ""
"Writing it this way suggests that there are several ways of cutting a"
" clip. This is in fact true."
msgstr ""

